#: ../../user_manual/working_with_text.rst:181
msgid "An alternative manner of putting text in a shape is to create a text, and a shape for it to flow in. Then, with the :ref:`shape_selection_tool` select both, and |mouseright| for the context menu. There, select :menuselection:`Text --> Flow Text in Shape`. If you have multiple shapes selected, you can flow the text into multiple shapes as well."
